data.description: ONE OF THE KIND HOUSE WITH 5 BEDROOMS AND 2,5 BATHROOMS AND 2 CAR GARAGE, 2 STORY. THIS HOME IS NESTLED WITHIN THE WELL-ESTABLISHED  COMMUNITY OF RIVER CROSSING ESTATE. WHEN YOU FIRST ENTER YOUR ATTENTION WILL IMMEDIATELY BE DRAWN TO SOARING HIGH CEILINGS, LARGE WINDOWS, AND A LOFT ON THE SECOND FLOOR. THE LARGE LIVING AND DINING ROOMS BOAST SLIDING GLASS DOORS THAT LEAD TO THE BACKYARD. SPACIOUS KITCHEN WITH A CENTERED ISLAND AND NEWER STAILING STILL APPLIANCES, A BREAKFAST AREA RIGHT NEXT TO THE KITCHEN WITH AN ENJOYABLE PATIO VIEW. THE LAUNDRY ROOM IS CONVENIENTLY  NEAR THE KITCHEN AND THE GARAGE. THE MASTER IS LOCATED IN THE FIRST FLOOR, AS WELL A GUESS ROOM. THE MASTER SUITE BOASTS A LARGE WALK-IN CLOSET AND A MASTER BATHROOM WITH A WALK-IN SHOWER, TUB, DUAL VANITIES. THE MASTER ALSO OFFERS SLIDING DOORS FACING THE BACKYARD. THREE MORE BEDROOMS ON THE SECOND FLOOR WITH A BATHROOM AND THE LOFT. ENJOY A HUGE FENCED BACKYARD WHERE YOU CAN PARK YOUR BOAT. NEW WATER HEATER. AC ABOUT 5 YEARS.  THE ROOF IS ABOUT 9 YEARS OLD. LOW HOA FEE. THIS HOME IS CLOSE TO GREAT SCHOOLS, SHOPPING, DINING AND MINUTES TO FL-60, US-301, AND I-75.
